MultiPixel Data Transparency Notice
Relimintor (Raptor4 / MultiPixel)

1. DATA MULTIPIXEL COLLECTS
• which servers a player joins
• when they join
• chat messages
• gameplay usage data

2. WHY WE COLLECT IT
• to improve user experience
• to improve safety
• to detect abuse
• to enforce rules
• to optimize gameplay

3. SERVER DATA COLLECTION
Approved servers may collect:
• join/leave logs
• chat logs

Servers may NOT collect:
• personal data
• payment information
• sensitive data

4. DATA RETENTION
• MultiPixel retains logs as needed for safety and improvement.
• Servers must retain logs for at least 90 days.

5. USER RIGHTS
Users may request:
• account deletion
• data review (if legally required)

6. SECURITY
MultiPixel uses reasonable measures to protect data.
